import React from 'react'
import { Box } from '@mui/material' 
import Post from './Post'

const Feed = () => {
  return (
    <Box bgcolor="red" flex={10} m>
        <Post/>
        <Post/>
        <Post/>
        <Post/>
        <Post/>
        <Post/>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Feed
